about.abouttext2: Banning Lewis Ranch is a beautiful Master Plan Community that has all the amenities you could ask for.  A recreational center with an Olympic size pool with 24 hr gym, splash park with a snack bar, parks & walking trails, dog park and 2 charter schools for Kindergarten all the way up to High School. You know you are home when you are here.
